> Mykhailivska: Articles from Ukraine's Constitution, UN Statute, and Bible
> verses are posted on the stanchions

At the time of writing this post, people continue to gather on Mykhailivska
Square in Kyiv, with rallies also taking place in Lviv and other cities.
Ustream user Myhajlivska has made [live stream
broadcast](http://www.ustream.tv/channel/myhajlivska) of protests from Kyiv
available through her account.

A nation-wide protest is called for Sunday, December 1, at noon.

